{"tid":452362,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你有一個咁既同事，你會如何應付？","createTime":"2017-10-30T06:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T06:35:23.000Z","uid":77769,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"aeff63e828b87aaf6b35a73792da8bfe199cef4b","tid":452362,"uid":77769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:40:35.000Z","msg":"呢個同事就 22-24歲既，做服務性行業<br />\n教佢最基本既野就教極佢都係唔識，無咩進展 (超過兩個月以上)<br />\n<br />\n又溝通唔到，好似同佢相隔幾個時代咁，幻想下你同你老母個種，得啦得啦 知啦知啦<br />\n<br />\n然後唔知到係那裡來的自信，天氣熱個陣間唔中會著d無袖既衫，短褲我都當睇唔到<br />\n重點係 喂喂喂，你加拿大有毛既，仲要唔係短既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n件衫又唔係長，間唔中仲會露埋條腰出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我求下你係公司入面著返件長袖衫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而且間中仲有d體臭<br />\n<br />\n利申：呢位同事係女性黎既，樣子方面更加唔洗期待，我已經放棄左教佢野，盡量都唔同佢有任何交流"},{"pid":"c0c6d2c37454a3538abce9d0c3325b65efaa5445","tid":452362,"uid":134367,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:44:45.000Z","msg":"服務性行業冇制服咩？"},{"pid":"6645bcc526530a70c61d9818cf496cb998f134a6","tid":452362,"uid":77769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:47:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>服務性行業冇制服咩？</blockquote><br />\n唔係間間有，服務性行業都有好多樣"},{"pid":"400ada33dcc4e45a13933f7dcdf75c8b87a3965f","tid":452362,"uid":77769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T07:39:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e168130805a05474f328ad3a910c681d38aa4227","tid":452362,"uid":93202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T07:41:25.000Z","msg":"咁你都講左唔理佢, 放棄左教佢<br />\n仲有咩好點應付先<br />\n咪等佢做錯野自動收皮囉"},{"pid":"b1be1f4baaef0c5e908a9eb4fddccfbaa7626533","tid":452362,"uid":77769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cited